*random number generator:
#include <time.h>  
srand(time(NULL)); 
int j = rand() % max_number; //generate a number between (0, max_number - 1)  

*reverse loop through an array:
wrong: for (size_t i = a_vector.size(); i >= 0; i--)
correct: for (int i = a_vector.size(); i >= 0; i--)

